{"tid":710627,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美退出人權理事會　《環時》批美人權很差「應搬到火星」","createTime":"2018-06-21T02:05:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T02:45:42.000Z","uid":39464,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"736979f37a92716acdc6933b69d827710ac5cdd0","tid":710627,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T02:05:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180621/s00004/3fc083cbc048573958adce4afc56317e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180621%2Fs00004%2F3fc083cbc048573958adce4afc56317e.jpg&h=1cc37307&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國昨宣布退出聯合國人權理事會，又點名批評中國、古巴等國家侵犯人權卻繼續獲選為人權理事會成員，斥責「人權理事會一直是侵犯人權者的保護者，並且是政治偏見的糞池」。中國官媒《環球時報》今日發表社評，批評美國人權做得很差，又認為美國應搬到火星。<br />\n<br />\n社評題為＜美國退出人權理事會還有理了＞，稱「單就人權問題來說，美國在很多方面做得很差」，如經常發生槍擊案，以及拆散人蛇家庭的「零容忍」政策等，「一說人權，只有它批評世界其他國家的份。什麼叫人權，什麼不能劃進人權裏，它說了算&hellip;&hellip;它不僅蠻橫，而且傲慢」。<br />\n<br />\n社評又說，美國先後退出巴黎氣候變化協定、聯合國教科文組織、伊朗核協議等，愈來愈不合群，「它似乎在地球上待着就很不自在，它應該整體搬到火星上去」。社評認為，美國應反思，「當它與多個聯合國機搆話不投機時，它自身一定出了什麼問題」。<br />\n<br />\n社評表示，人權問題是美國和西方攻擊中國主要方向之一，但看到今次事件，應了解西方操弄人權話題時的「裝腔作勢」，稱「如果我們被與聯合國人權理事會格格不入的力量左右了，將是多麼大的悲哀」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180621/s00004/1529542102761\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180621%2Fs00004%2F1529542102761&d=aoqUoJv2Fu3xeYwg8hDTi2owyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=0d397c91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180621%2Fs00004%2F1529542102761&h=e8e4a857\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180621/s00004/1529542102761</a>"},{"pid":"de5d04e49e6e250a19b128cfb8a2fe64e5adec7c","tid":710627,"uid":51701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T02:06:01.000Z","msg":"中國人權是最好的"},{"pid":"9e72e7ebcdd0c7b91a013fb257fd55ce03142bc8","tid":710627,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T02:07:13.000Z","msg":"噉支那係咪要搬離太陽系?"},{"pid":"04900f8d73cdac6b6901c0b11356404813e3c110","tid":710627,"uid":118973,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T02:07:51.000Z","msg":"屌  又贏"},{"pid":"40c545be08bf664897df76a2b0abc3c1cc5ada54","tid":710627,"uid":84975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T02:07:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9326ed09fadf8390b316d124a8f62db60ec81e16","tid":710627,"uid":152123,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T02:08:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/9rWmUuwkNQvra/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F9rWmUuwkNQvra%2Fgiphy.gif&h=337d65f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ac4fa97919172f9f9c8424dc0bcb105ce1f06ee","tid":710627,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9326ed09fadf8390b316d124a8f62db60ec81e16","tid":710627,"uid":152123,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T02:08:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/9rWmUuwkNQvra/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F9rWmUuwkNQvra%2Fgiphy.gif&h=337d65f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T02:09:30.000Z","msg":"睇親都笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6416058d73d05b03949ef54a1bb10738c97febbe","tid":710627,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T02:11:44.000Z","msg":"唔反省同認錯比到中國人幾大既樂趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/101142_78c20ee93088b2e1985985459c81d861.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F101142_78c20ee9308